pesticide.PPE: Long-sleeved shirt and long pants; Gloves; Shoes and socks

Active_Ingredients.name: LCO SP104
Active_Ingredients.mode_Of_Action: Stimulates germination of mycorrhizal spores and promotes mycorrhizal symbioses

Safety_Information.general_Info: Caution. Wash hands thoroughly with soap and water after handling and before eating, drinking, chewing gum, using tobacco or using the toilet. Wear the appropriate Personal Protective Equipment (PPE). Remove and wash contaminated clothing before reuse.
